\f1\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'95
\f2\b Key Technical Details
\f3\b0\fs24 \

\f1\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'95
\f4 Framework: 
\f2\b PyTorch
\f4\b0  (not MATLAB) \'97 needed for autograd through the emulator in Stage 2
\f3\fs24 \

\f1\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'95
\f4 Architecture: MLP with 4\'d7256 hidden layers, GELU activation, LayerNorm, dropout=0.1
\f3\fs24 \

\f1\fs18\fsmilli9333 \'95
\f4 Output activation: Sigmoid scaled to physical bounds [1, 25] \uc0\u956 m for r_e and [3, 30] for \u964 _c
\f3\fs24 \

